name: Naresh Nath Yogi
description: In her classroom at a leading educational institution in Kathmandu, Priya creates an engaging and interactive learning environment. Her teaching philosophy revolves around making complex IT concepts accessible to students at various levels of expertise. She employs a variety of teaching methods, including hands-on projects, case studies, and collaborative group activities, fostering an atmosphere where curiosity and exploration are encouraged.
